Package: gdl
Title: Graph Package Download Counts
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Douglas Ezra", "Morrison", , "demorrison@ucdavis.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Plot new and cumulative download counts for an R package
    over time, combining CRAN download data (via the packageRank
    package) with optional GitHub Releases asset-download counts.
    Supports configurable time-unit aggregation and start-date
    filtering, and exposes the data layer via a custom S3 class with
    an autoplot() method.
